snippet.title: Toree's Panic Pack - Trailer
snippet.description:
Three Tiny Toree Games in one! Two completely new ones developed by Kalliros are coming to Steam, Itch, and Switch together with Toree Genesis FINALLY making its debut on Switch and Steam!

Nintendo Switch: - July 19th -
Itch:                        - July 19th -
Steam:                   - July 22nd -

Wishlist on Steam: 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3089290/Torees_Panic_Pack/
